 \frac{d}{dx}\log\left(e^{\alpha x+\beta}+e^{\gamma x+\delta}\right) =\frac{\alpha e^{\alpha x+\beta}+\gamma e^{\gamma x+\delta}}{e^{\alpha x+\beta}+e^{\gamma x+\delta}} =\gamma+\frac{\alpha -\gamma  }{1+e^{(\gamma-\alpha) x+\delta-\beta}} 
